tedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T08:46:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4252d5bb6be3cf6ae6e3f84473cb4bf1cab8d8a","tid":470020,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T08:46:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>痴撚線 萬五蚊凈係住到狗竇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲鬼佬見到會點諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n萬五蚊租到美孚新村四百零呎 交通唔會輸比西灣河<br />\n條女係要住新樓冇辦法</blockquote><br />\n港島就係港島</blockquote><br />\n間屋你既咩 港島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd1bb9346afec444972eb1ee79cd37b56035a8fa","tid":470020,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T08:54:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>200呎間到房？</blockquote><br />\n230呎間到兩房，咁200呎間到一房有咩出奇？<br />\n沙士年49萬買西環納米盤　業主狂賺近9倍離場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/429374/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/429374/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dab6584ee600dd00be2eb8d8b0ce225e171238b2","tid":470020,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T08:57:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>200呎間到房？</blockquote><br />\n236呎間到兩房兩廳添<br />\n<br />\n沙田圍大把呢d啦 大驚小怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa6dcc987b9adc5f2cb350a414de58ce4b288dd4","tid":470020,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T08:58:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>200呎間到房？</blockquote><br />\n230呎間到兩房，咁200呎間到一房有咩出奇？<br />\n沙士年49萬買西環納米盤　業主狂賺近9倍離場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/429374/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/429374/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</blockquote><br />\n金獅花園282呎單位 間4房<br />\n<br />\n大圍上車屋苑金獅花園G座一個單位，雖然實用面積只有282方呎，但成功間出一間主人房、兩間客房，以及一個儲物室！<br />\n<br />\n單位其中一個設計人── 來自cMoneyHome的裝修監督工程及驗樓師Ann，解釋設計概念來源：「大家一向覺得只有200多呎的「蝸居」一定要做開放式單位，我們就想運用設計技巧，做一個新嘗試，看看能否將這個原本只有兩房的單位，變成有更多房間、有更多私隱，同時又有很大的活動空間呢？」"},{"pid":"cef90cbdf9fec1b94c0c72f96bb90720b4714429","tid":470020,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T09:05:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f789b232e0ca686b363ea45c91f4f2e2612f0ecb","tid":470020,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T09:39:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c7454309c8774329e2e020e2719e9cf0de6d826d","tid":470020,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T10:09:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a5ac55916db8d65b6759c447b8e0685e7218424","tid":470020,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T10:23:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90bba863406f118f8d1def47628debf3c33d8bc9","tid":470020,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T10:27:15.000Z","msg":"Q房網<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b37a59b9cfba60c03598b28322a7558a9cf6906","tid":470020,"uid":47202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T10:31:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>皇帝都係訓張床啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n叫我?"},{"pid":"9ed1faed15a67adc5a65000ac6631b0bb6c45f67","tid":470020,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T10:33:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3bcaeaa89f74a874e336ee221d567638fc083b90","tid":470020,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20